iorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=637.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: maybe i'm not understanding???</span><hr size=1> As no one specifically mentioned it, taunt does not work on yellow or higher conning mobs pre-60.  Hit the button to your hearts content, it doesn't do anything.<br><br>At 55 he won't be hit for maximum damage often, where you would get hit for max damage consistanly due to level/defense skill.  Reavers are nasty <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/umahulkkeras.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mahulk Keras</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/9/02 6:53:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=637.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: maybe i'm not understanding???</span><hr size=1> Levels &gt; anything else<br>Levels after 50 means even more. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2504 target=blank>Mahulk Keras</a><br><a href=http://www.titansofsaryrn.com target=blank>Titans of Saryrn</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ushikariiapoccalypse.showPublicProfile?language=E